title: Street Fighter 6 Announced! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 02.21.22
description:
Kahlief joins a picture of Tim to talk Street Fighter 6, Capcom Fighting Collection, Master Chief taking off his helmet in the Halo show, the Uncharted movie box office, and more!

Follow Kahlief at https://twitter.com/KahliefAdams
